name: Super Jacked Up Tomato Face Johnson
overview: Super Jacked Up Tomato Face Johnson is a fast paced twitch platformer made for the Game Boy Color. There's a new protein shake fresh on the shelves and Tomato Face Johnson needs to bulk up! It's on the pricey side of course, but luckily, it's on sale for a limited time... Time to get speedy! Collect all the coins to complete levels. Complete levels super fast and you will earn enough stars to progress to the next world.
